title: O'NEILL MUTANT 2013/14
description: Accept no limitations. O'Neill's unique Modular Closure system makes the Mutant the most versatile wetsuit in our line. Now with an easier entry and new graphics. The 2013 Mutant has been completely updated to 100% UltraFlex DS and UltraFlex Firewall in the front and back. Making the Mutant is now warmer and more flexible than ever before. Two suits in one, now go get some.
